quran[45]{c,v,t}:
  36,60,‘ELEM ‘A’HED ‘ILEJKUM JA BENI ‘ADEME ‘EN LA TA’BUDU ESH-SHEJTANE ‘INNEHU LEKUM ‘ADUWUN MUBINUN
  36,61,WE ‘ENI A’BUDUNI HADHA SIRATUN MUSTEKIMUN
  36,62,WE LEKAD ‘EDELLE MINKUM XHIBILLÆN KETHIRÆN ‘EFELEM TEKUNU TA’KILUNE
  36,63,HEDHIHI XHEHENNEMU ELLETI KUNTUM TU’ADUNE
  36,64,ESLEWHAL-JEWME BIMA KUNTUM TEKFURUNE
  36,65,EL-JEWME NEHTIMU ‘ALA ‘EFWAHIHIM WE TUKELLIMUNA ‘EJDIHIM WE TESH/HEDU ‘ERXHULUHUM BIMA KANU JEKSIBUNE
  36,66,WE LEW NESHA’U LETEMESNA ‘ALA ‘A’JUNIHIM FASTEBEKU ES-SIRATE FE’ENNA JUBSIRUNE
  36,67,WE LEW NESHA’U LEMESEHNAHUM ‘ALA MEKANETIHIM FEMA ESTETA’U MUDIJÆN WE LA JERXHI’UNE
  36,68,WE MEN NU’AMMIRHU NUNEKKIS/HU FIL-HALKI ‘EFELA JA’KILUNE
  36,69,WE MA ‘ALLEMNAHU ESH-SHI’RE WE MA JENBEGI LEHU ‘IN HUWE ‘ILLA DHIKRUN WE KUR’ANUN MUBINUN
  36,70,LIJUNDHIRE MEN KANE HEJJÆN WE JEHIKKAL-KAWLU ‘ALEL-KAFIRINE
  36,71,‘EWELEM JEREW ‘ENNA HALEKNA LEHUM MIMMA ‘AMILET ‘EJDINA ‘EN’AMÆN FEHUM LEHA MALIKUNE
  36,72,WE DHELLELNAHA LEHUM FEMINHA REKUBUHUM WE MINHA JE’KULUNE
  36,73,WE LEHUM FIHA MENAFI’U WE MESHARIBU ‘EFELA JESHKURUNE
  36,74,WE ETTEHADHU MIN DUNI ELLAHI ‘ALIHETEN LE’ALLEHUM JUNSERUNE
  36,75,LA JESTETI’UNE NESREHUM WE HUM LEHUM XHUNDUN MUHDERUNE
  36,76,FELA JEHZUNKE KAWLUHUM ‘INNA NA’LEMU MA JUSIRRUNE WE MA JU’LINUNE
  36,77,‘EWELEM JEREL-’INSANU ‘ENNA HALEKNAHU MIN NUTFETIN FE’IDHA HUWE HASIMUN MUBINUN
  36,78,WE DEREBE LENA METHELÆN WE NESIJE HALKAHU KALE MEN JUHJIL-’IDHAME WE HIJE REMIMUN
  36,79,KUL JUHJIHAL-LEDHI ‘ENSHE’EHA ‘EWWELE MERRETIN WE HUWE BIKULLI HALKIN ‘ALIMUN
  36,80,EL-LEDHI XHE’ALE LEKUM MINE ESH-SHEXHERIL-’EHDERI NARÆN FE’IDHA ‘ENTUM MINHU TUKIDUNE
  36,81,‘EWELEJSEL-LEDHI HALEKA ES-SEMAWATI WEL-’ERDE BIKADIRIN ‘ALA ‘EN JEHLUKA MITHLEHUM BELA WE HUWEL-HALLAKUL-’ALIMU
  36,82,‘INNEMA ‘EMRUHU ‘IDHA ‘ERADE SHEJ’ÆN ‘EN JEKULE LEHU KUN FEJEKUNU
  36,83,FESUBHANEL-LEDHI BIJEDIHI MELEKUTU KULLI SHEJ’IN WE ‘ILEJHI TURXHA’UNE
  37,1,WE ES-SAFFATI SEFFÆN
  37,2,FALZZAXHIRATI ZEXHRÆN
  37,3,FALTTALIJATI DHIKRÆN
  37,4,‘INNE ‘ILEHEKUM LEWAHIDUN
  37,5,REBBU ES-SEMAWATI WEL-’ERDI WE MA BEJNEHUMA WE REBBUL-MESHARIKI
  37,6,‘INNA ZEJJENNA ES-SEMA’E ED-DUNJA BIZINETINL-KEWAKIB
  37,7,WE HIFDHÆN MIN KULLI SHEJTANIN MARIDIN
  37,8,LA JESSEMMA’UNE ‘ILAL-MELE’IL-’A’LA WE JUKDHEFUNE MIN KULLI XHANIBIN
  37,9,DUHURÆN WE LEHUM ‘ADHABUN WE ESIBUN
  37,10,‘ILLA MEN HATIFEL-HATFETE FE’ETBE’AHU SHIHABUN THAKIBUNA
  37,11,FASTEFTIHIM ‘EHUM ‘ESHEDDU HALKÆN ‘EM MEN HALEKNA ‘INNA HALEKNAHUM MIN TININ LAZIBIN
  37,12,BEL ‘AXHIBTE WE JESHARUNE
  37,13,WE ‘IDHA DHUKKIRU LA JEDHKURUNE
  37,14,WE ‘IDHA RE’EW ‘AJETEN JESTESHIRUNE
  37,15,WE KALU ‘IN HADHA ‘ILLA SIHRUN MUBINUN
  37,16,‘E’IDHA MITNA WE KUNNA TURABÆN WE ‘IDHAMÆN ‘E’INNA LEMEB’UTHUNE
  37,17,‘EWE’ABA’UUNAL-’EWWELUNE
  37,18,KUL NE’AM WE ‘ENTUM DAHIRUNE
  37,19,FE’INNEMA HIJE ZEXHRETUN WAHIDETUN FE’IDHA HUM JENDHURUNE
  37,20,WE KALU JA WEJLENA HADHA JEWMU ED-DINI
  37,21,HADHA JEWMUL-FESLIL-LEDHI KUNTUM BIHI TUKEDHDHIBUNE